snippet.title: Zac Efron and Amber Heard Autobahn Co-Stars!
snippet.description:
Zac Efron and Amber Heard New Movie - Autobahn! Full details and sneak peek!
http://bit.ly/SubClevverNews - Subscribe Now!
http://Twitter.com/ClevverNews - Follow Us!
http://Twitter.com/Katie_Krause - Send Katie a Tweet!
http://Facebook.com/ClevverNews - Like Us!
http://Clevver.com - Visit our site!
Zac is joining actress Amber Heard in a new car-chase thrilled called Autobahn.  The news was announced at the Cannes Film Festival -- and we here at Clevver are stoked to see this duo on the big screen together. 
As for what the movie is about -- Zac will play an American backpacker who gets hired to work as a pickup driver for a gang of German drug smugglers.  But, when the job doesn't quite go as planned, he's forced to flee from the gang -- and from there, viewers will be taken on an adventure of high-speed chases and dramatic action sequences as Zac fights his way out of trouble.
Amber Heard, lucky girl, will play his on-screen girlfriend. 
Filming is slated to shoot this fall on location in Germany.
Now, Zac has been quite the busy fella lately.  He's current;y filming the comedy Townies -- alongside Seth Rogen and Dave Franco.  We'll also catch him in the upcoming rom-com "Are We Officially Dating?" -- expect to hit theaters later this year... AND, he also has a film called Parkland which just wrapped production, too.  
Busy. Busy. Busy. 
Let me know what you guys think of this new movie -- are you excited to see Zac in this kind of action-packed and slightly darker role than usual.... Do you think he and Amber will have good on-screen chemistry?  Or, are you so not into this?
Let me know what you're thinking by commenting or by tweeting.... Or hey, you can do both.  And then of course thumbs up this video, cause I know you love Zac -- and of course SUBSCRIBE if you haven't done so already.
In Hollywood, I'm your host Katie Krause and thanks for watching!
